General.Name: GCH Technology Co. Ltd. A
General.Description: GCH Technology Co., Ltd. researches, develops, produces, and sells nucleating agents, synthetic hydrotalcites, and composite additives in China, and internationally. The company's product portfolio includes clarifier for polyolefine, high-performance nucleators, ß-type nucleators, and PA nucleators; acid scavenger for PVC and polyolefine; non-dust one-pack, a granular type of additive mixture; preblend additives; masterbatch additives for resins; primary and secondary antioxidant; light stabilizers and UV absorbers; and anti-block agents. It serves food and beverage packaging, household appliance, auto parts, toys, wire and cable, medical supplies, artificial leather industries, as well as profiles, tube, and pipe industries. GCH Technology Co., Ltd. was founded in 2002 and is headquartered in Guangzhou, China.
